description.narrative: UNICEF Venezuela strengthened its operational structure to provide an adequate and timely response to implement the Scale Up Program and Humanitarian Response in 2019. The structure of the Operations Area was reinforced with qualified and experienced staff, these staff worked closely with the Regional Office, DFAM, Supply Division and the GSSC. Three Field Offices were opened to expedite the programmatic and operational response in the frontier. Internal coordination mechanisms were strengthened. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:10/02/2020
